it.emarolab.owloop.descriptor.construction.descriptorExpression

Interface ObjectPropertyExpression

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Axiom, Axiom.Descriptor<it.emarolab.amor.owlInterface.OWLReferences,org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLObjectProperty>, Axiom.Ground<it.emarolab.amor.owlInterface.OWLReferences,org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLObjectProperty>, DescriptorGroundInterface<org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLObjectProperty>, ObjectProperty<it.emarolab.amor.owlInterface.OWLReferences,org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLObjectProperty>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ObjectPropertyExpression.Disjoint<D>, ObjectPropertyExpression.Domain, ObjectPropertyExpression.Equivalent<D>, ObjectPropertyExpression.Inverse<D>, ObjectPropertyExpression.Range, ObjectPropertyExpression.Sub<D>, ObjectPropertyExpression.Super<D>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefinitionObjectPropertyDesc, DomainRangeObjectPropertyDesc, FullObjectPropertyDesc, HierarchicalObjectPropertyDesc, ObjectPropertyGround

    public interface ObjectPropertyExpression
extends ObjectProperty<it.emarolab.amor.owlInterface.OWLReferences,org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLObjectProperty>, DescriptorGroundInterface<org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLObjectProperty>
    This interface extends all the interfaces in ObjectProperty. It allows to Axiom.Descriptor.readExpressionAxioms() and Axiom.Descriptor.writeExpressionAxioms() specifically for OWL DataProperties. It contains several expressions that can be combined in any arbitrary way as they rely on the same ground (ObjectGroundInstance).
